craterdog.security

Class NotaryKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • craterdog.security.NotaryKey

  • public final class NotaryKey
extends Object
    This class defines the attributes associated with a notary key. A notary key has a private part (signing key) that is used to sign notarized documents. It also has a public part (verification key) that is used to verify that a document was signed using the notary key.
    Author:
    Derk Norton
